  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 0,
  "id": null,
  "links": [],
  "liveNow": false,
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "How to read this dashboard",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0,
        "w": 24,
        "h": 4
      },
      "options": {
        "content": "**Time picker affects all Prometheus panels**: API load, latency, pool pressure, PostgreSQL pressure, and ranked endpoint lists.  \n**SQL DBA panels are current snapshots** from PostgreSQL/Pangolin: they show the database state *right now* (sessions, waits, locks, hot tables).  \n\nThe most important ranked lists are already visible directly:\n- **Best cache candidates** — read methods with the highest traffic-weighted cost\n- **Heaviest methods overall** — the biggest practical load on the API/DB path\n- **Slowest methods by p95** — unstable or tail-heavy endpoints\n- **Slow write methods** — likely not cache candidates",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {},
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "API RPS",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
      },
      "description": "Overall incoming request rate.",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 4,
        "w": 4,
        "h": 4
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(http_server_requests_seconds_count{job=~\"$job_app\",uri!~\".*actuator.*\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "refId": "A",
          "instant": true,
          "legendFormat": "__auto"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "reqps",
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 0
              }
            ]
          },
          "decimals": 2
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "values": false,
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": ""
        },
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "showPercentChange": false
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "API p95 latency",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
      },
      "description": "Overall API p95 response time.",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 4,
        "y": 4,
        "w": 4,
        "h": 4
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (le) (rate(http_server_requests_seconds_bucket{job=~\"$job_app\",uri!~\".*actuator.*\"}[$__rate_interval])))",
          "refId": "A",
          "instant": true,
          "legendFormat": "__auto"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s",
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 0
              }
            ]
          },
          "decimals": 3
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "values": false,
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": ""
        },
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "showPercentChange": false
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Pool utilization",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
      },
      "description": "Application-side DB connection pool utilization.",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 8,
        "y": 4,
        "w": 4,
        "h": 4
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(jdbc_connections_active{job=~\"$job_app\"}) / clamp_min(sum(jdbc_connections_max{job=~\"$job_app\"}),1)",
          "refId": "A",
          "instant": true,
          "legendFormat": "__auto"
